                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                                        <date>\n                                                  <hi rend=\"underline\">5614</hi>\n                                        </date>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                                        <placeName>St Thomas</placeName>\n                                        <date>14 Ap 1854</date>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>\n                                        <addressee>Revd Mr Leeser</addressee>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>\n                                        <placeName>Phila</placeName>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Dear Sir</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(2)\">I am in receipt of your esteemed<lb/> letter of\n                                        the <date>2d</date> In. annexing Invoice of Bibles,\n                                        Prayer<lb/> Books &amp;c. which shall be attended to after\n                                        the sailing<lb/> of the Packet as I have no time to attend\n                                        to the<lb/> collection during her stay. The Congregation\n                                        has<lb/> paid me $12 for advertising in the Occident.</p>\n                              <p>I enclose <add>?</add> it Green agent of the Pa<add>?</add><lb/>\n                                        Rail Road Co on its President for Two hundred &amp;\n                                        seventy<lb/> five dollars which I advance you &amp; please\n                                        credit it<lb/> me for ten of the bibles are undeliver'd,\n                                        parties who<lb/> subscribed for them being absent from the\n                                                  <placeName>Island</placeName>.</p>\n                              <p>I have not seen <persName>Mr Car<add>?</add></persName> yet.<lb/>\n                                        My Son <persName>Mr Moses Wolff</persName> of\n                                                  <placeName>Laguayra<add>?</add></placeName> his\n                                        wife 2 sons<lb/> with his sister in law <persName>Mrs\n                                                  Jeller</persName> &amp; her daughter take<lb/>\n                                        passage in this steamer to reside in <placeName>New\n                                                  York</placeName>, may I<lb/> ask your attention to\n                                        them.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(4)\">Truly Dr Sir</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(5)\">yours</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(6)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">A.Wolff</persName>\n                              </p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p34f1n455/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
